                    <p>I buy (good, like Boars Head) roast beef from the deli sliced super thin, buy a packet of Au Jus, simmer it, then slap some hot giardiniera from a jar on it.  10 minutes, you're done.  And we're from Chicago.  But your way sounds good too.  :-)</p>
