    <h3 class="tape">

        About this Entry


    </h3>
    <div class="widget-content">
<p>Welcome to the Food in my Beard!  I save stuff for later.  if you want to know more about me, check out <a href="/about-me">these posts</a>, otherwise feel free to browse around and get hungry! </p>


        <p class="first">This post by The Food in my Beard was published on <em>March  3, 2009 10:54 AM</em>.</p>
    
        <p><a href="http://www.thefoodinmybeard.com/2009/03/peanut-butter-smore-cake.html">Peanut Butter S'more Cake</a> was yesterday.</p>
    
    
        <p><a href="http://www.thefoodinmybeard.com/2009/03/last-restaurant-standing---flags-of-the-world-1.html">Last Restaurant Standing - Flags of the World</a> is tomorrow.</p>
    





        <p>Newest recipes are on the <a href="http://www.thefoodinmybeard.com/">front page</a> or look in the <a href="http://www.thefoodinmybeard.com/archives.html">archives</a> to find all content.</p>

